{"tid":1987096,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣戰報】手足創作的關於反送中的書，佔據Kindle繁體中文書排行榜第一名","createTime":"2020-04-24T08:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T08:53:17.000Z","uid":48040,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eddcf72c35247968d6849a7650aa518153d06800","tid":1987096,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T08:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GYa2q1L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGYa2q1L.png&h=1f4ae341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚出Post之後，得到眾多手足支持，成功將手足寫的關於反送中的書推上了<span style=\"color: red;\">Kindle繁體中文書排行榜第一名</span>。十分感謝大家。特別係post入面的每一位手足。<br />\n<br />\n請容許我再不厭其煩地講多次係呢個時勢，寫書、買書、看書的重要性。上個月，港共最近出版咗本書叫《哭泣的城市》，肆意抹黑抗爭運動。最弊係，港共掌握了全港連鎖書店，令到所有出入書店的學生及市民都很可能遭受洗腦。長此下去，歷史可能被改寫，正義會被掩蓋。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地絕唔可以坐以待斃，絕不能係書籍呢個文宣領域中敗給敵人。誰掌握了書，誰就掌握了歷史。誰掌握了歷史，誰就掌握了未來。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，希望大家幫手share及廣傳呢本書。比我更有學識、文筆更好的手足大有人在，而呢本書假如得到廣傳，相信可以起到拋磚引玉的作用，吸引更多有識之士參與創作、百花齊放。到時，成個kindle排行榜可能全部都係反送中的書。到時，我們就掌握了歷史的書寫權。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>《權力多面睇》Link:</strong></ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B087G3LZCH/ref=cm_sw_r_tw_dp_U_x_BBQOEbNQEPT2J\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB087G3LZCH%2Fref%3Dcm_sw_r_tw_dp_U_x_BBQOEbNQEPT2J&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn3f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=5c035237\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/dp/B087G3LZCH/ref=cm_sw_r_tw_dp_U_x_BBQOEbNQEPT2J</a><br />\n<ins><strong>Facebook Post:</strong></ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107615530931591/posts/107684360924708/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107615530931591%2Fposts%2F107684360924708%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn3f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=f15eb26d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107615530931591/posts/107684360924708/?d=n</a><br />\n<ins><strong>我們的Youtube Channel: </strong></ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCulMs0FGwozR1mj1a7-BuDw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCulMs0FGwozR1mj1a7-BuDw%2F&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn3f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=51e0647b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCulMs0FGwozR1mj1a7-BuDw/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRQazYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRQazYD.jpg&h=dfe79dbb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}